### EduPortal API - Academic Terms Controller
### Academic term management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/academicTerms
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL ACADEMIC TERMS - Paginated list
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET TERM BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACTIVE TERM
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE ACADEMIC TERM - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "2024-2025 Güz Dönemi",
  "academicYear": "2024-2025",
  "semester": 1,
  "startDate": "2024-09-02",
  "endDate": "2025-01-17",
  "isActive": false
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE ACADEMIC TERM - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "2024-2025 Güz Dönemi (Güncellenmiş)",
  "startDate": "2024-09-09",
  "endDate": "2025-01-24"
}

### ===========================================
### ACTIVATE ACADEMIC TERM - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### DELETE ACADEMIC TERM - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
